<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>60: Five tens and 1 ten make 6 tens, which is 60.</li>
      <li>62: It’s just like the first one, but there are 2 ones so it would be 62.</li>
      <li>73: It’s like the second problem, but there’s 1 more ten and 1 more one. So each one goes up by 1 so it’s 73.</li>
      <li>78: There are 7 tens and 8 ones so it’s 78.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


